Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.20,0:01:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了五月 有什么可以采收的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.10,0:01:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…红萝卜、芜菁、韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有草莓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于到时候了 好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.79,0:01:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 好期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.22,0:01:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 都已经四月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.13,0:01:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过今天却有点冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也马上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.43,0:01:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子也饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.87,0:02:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客气 先回去做饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.74,0:02:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那天在学校见过慊人之后经过了几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.85,0:02:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过由希依然很开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午餐要煮什么好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 这该不会是十二生肖里的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}音同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服里面好像有东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈的 肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透应该马上就回来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 你来做点东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 阿夹 我看先这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就先把菜挑好 等他们回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊 就算无聊也别这样搞我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能这样浪费食物喔 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁理你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 回来了…咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在马上剥了这条蛇的皮 弄个烧烤来吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫…绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.30,0:03:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是绫女吗 怎么突然来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上剥了他的皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 别激动 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩绫女 就像你所看到的他是条蛇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是绫女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛇不是会冬眠吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是这样 绫女也很怕冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像今天这种冷天很容易就会变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.12,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女跟我和波鸟同年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小学、国中到高中一直都在一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换句话说 三个人在一起就成了花般耀眼三人组了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样呀 原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么啊 什么花般耀眼三人组啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前浮现波鸟痛苦的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 刚才由希为什么那么生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在是烦死人了 我连提都不想提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂喂 不可以这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.64,0:04:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对自己的亲哥哥这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥…哥哥…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就由我自己来说明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才我身体冻僵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在寻找暖身的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时正好有人过来 就不知不觉的跟着对方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想这就是所谓的本能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 还有我亲爱的弟弟 过得好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像长大后的由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么不知不觉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你该庆幸还好没被抓进警察局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊 他对你做了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 夹竹桃你也在这里呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少这样叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不管夹竹桃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这样叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见啦 紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.54,0:05:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不在的期间 你没有拈花惹草吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你在 我哪可能做那种事呢 绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.82,0:05:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来和由希的个性不太一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来介绍 她就是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是来找她的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.06,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才真是失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是由希的亲哥哥绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好 初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此…原来如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的像女王一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这邋遢男人窝中唯一的一朵花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像被困住的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可没困住她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥 你别捉弄人家行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.09,0:06:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太失礼了 我可是很尊敬她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女王 首先给我一杯茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午餐也快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里尊敬呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还真难伺候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 我们去外面吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么好考虑的 我请客！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我生气也没用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 尽管点你喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.05,0:06:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便 我要水饺定食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用挂意由希他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是小孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们会自己弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我一直受他们照顾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.40,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都说要请客了 难道你不捧场吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 完全没这回事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.17,0:06:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老板 给我两份水饺定食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都他决定了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过真让人惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希从来没说过他有哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没说过你是十二生肖的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没说是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如你所看到的 我们的感情不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 应该说是不亲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年纪也差了10岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希一出生又因为有病在身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因而被隔离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔离？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我也有不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于这个弟弟的存在总是毫不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直按着自己的方式抚育他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我发现问题时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们之间已有很深的代沟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希在学校时不是碰到了慊人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你当时也在场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,详情我也很难说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之对由希来说 慊人是个可怕的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他现在一定很消沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说是来见你 但应该说是来看由希的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果发现他还挺有精神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.31,0:08:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老实说心里松了一口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然说我不是个好哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.68,0:08:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于你们之间的代沟 你后悔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思议的是 人随着年龄的增长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.32,0:08:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小时候不懂的事慢慢就会了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时应该这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时应该这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢都会了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.43,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我与其说是后悔 倒不如说是忏悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许是想藉着忏悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.31,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去否认自己以前的年幼无知吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样 所以人家都说大人很自私吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈曾经这么说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.42,0:08:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要等到自己为人父母才开始了解天下父母心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是其实最该了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最不可以忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小时候的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次学会吊单杠的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次被骂得很惨的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有孩提时候感受到的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够好好的记住的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算长大成人也能够互相理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即便无法完全做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少也能靠近那种心境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这种想法会让人比较快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.23,0:09:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我想说的只是…也就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.07,0:09:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和由希今后一定会有所进展的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得真是好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 我妈妈是宇宙最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我说的是你啦…算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我终于明白由希为什么那么有精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 我和由希才要开始吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也努力看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.54,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后也请你继续做由希的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时的绫女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 大家午餐吃了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是我哥哥有没有困扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有 还请我吃水饺定食呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讨厌你哥哥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 只是问问而已 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与其说是讨厌…应该是难搞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在不知道他在想些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难搞的话 好好克服就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.35,0:11:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正是我们亲近的时候 弟弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一离开店面后 天气突然又冷起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以又变回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说要是太冷的话 蛇会死掉的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁叫我是蛇嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才不是我哥哥 我跟你没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实是无法改变的！由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们回来了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.78,0:11:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时的绫女流露了哥哥的微笑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 今晚我睡哪儿呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？你要住下来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续睡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为由希把门锁上不让我进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你去紫吴的房间睡嘛 就像昨天那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但紫吴不让我跟他睡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 儿童不宜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底要待到什么时候呀\N不听！不闻！不问！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈…不必伤脑筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚我要睡小透那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滚回去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女来后第三天的早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.45,0:12:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但和弟弟由希的代沟却似乎愈来愈深了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 绫女来了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从过年后就没再见过他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去找他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但会打扰到他们兄弟团聚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希怎么样？高兴吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希生病了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但绫女是店长 放着店面不管好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？绫女在开店吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.73,0:13:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是卖一些护士、空姐、女仆等的服饰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是洋装店吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女说是一间贩卖男人梦想的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 你们很厉害唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.78,0:13:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就从学校回来 那么想跟我说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒很想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.32,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独处呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是担心这个才赶回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在看什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们以前高中时期的相簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 波鸟也在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴和波鸟都很年轻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女也和现在的由希好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.14,0:14:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有朝气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女从这时起就留长发了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 虽然违反校规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 你也看一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是了解你哥哥的绝好机会喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.03,0:14:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是非要我说明为何学校允许我留长发了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 就在入学后不久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有天我突然被校长叫住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本是自己想说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.17,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发色虽然允许了 但我可没说可以留长发喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天以前去把它剪掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.21,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,校长 我是王族的后代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都没告诉别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我有天得回到我的国家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说为何我们王族非留长发不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说第一代国王鲁鲁巴拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在满四岁时曾接受神的告诫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.83,0:15:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四方放着刺有金与红光的卡多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当颂为马鲁多穆尼的卡多拉额上出现青光时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鲁鲁巴拉的身体就仿佛鞭策过的骏马般得到解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.94,0:15:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随着满怀的慈爱 头发如沐春风般飘逸起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到众所周知的卡司巴鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.35,0:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本已如带芽的花般在御所安息着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪知胸部突然发出卡巴尼鲁的高鸣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等…对不起…我待会还有会面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡多拉的事我还没说完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了 要留长发就留吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样才可以留长发的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是王族的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是胡说的罗 猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好怀念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.71,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那再讲一个你不敢相信的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女可是学生会长喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别耍宝了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之总会有人看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.59,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟史无前例的绫女的行为总是引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是校规 活动等也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了绫女那一代后变得颇具变化而有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是因为他真的有实力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.17,0:16:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我倒认为波鸟比我更适合当学生会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还记得吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕业旅行那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能忘记呢 绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这好像可以让由希对绫女产生兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正是缩短彼此距离的机会 绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 当时呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.76,0:16:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有部份学生在旅行中涉足了声色场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欸 先别急着骂人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身体健康的男人谁都会想进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我们可没去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为已不是稀奇事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得还真轻松呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不幸地是 这件事被老师知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们全部被告知会遭到退学的处分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然身为学生会长的我也提出了抗议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在学生 家长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,校长与老师之间进行了协调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们虽然未成年却涉足声色场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的行为当然不足以为取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有法律就得遵守 否则秩序将会大乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但将性欲这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当作是坏事般的全盘否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对此点感到相当遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为许多人背负着传宗接代的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.65,0:17:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我认为性欲是担任此使命的一端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这有那么可耻 罪恶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的绫女比平常还认真呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常的他果然只是装疯卖傻而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我在这里有个建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这未成年的尴尬年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.50,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该拯救这群无处发泄欲望的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.01,0:18:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后请把各位的欲望发泄在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为学生代表的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,承担大家的欲望也是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.38,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且对男学生的家长来说这样也比较放心安全吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 尽情发泄你们的欲望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若以接受与攻击来比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是接受者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是猪头呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.53,0:18:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然脑筋有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是无可救药的白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈 不需要多虑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然像我这样子 不过我可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这件伟大的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看是蠢事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太失礼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因为这样 所以大家都免于遭到退学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.24,0:18:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为波鸟后来帮忙擦屁股罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后就这样 到毕业都是绫女当会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.68,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样？由希 对哥哥是否有点了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滚出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代沟 代沟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就来讲理事长铜像的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了 你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是某个夏日的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 想想办法解决这家伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？不是挺愉快的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呀 很愉快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们很痛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.86,0:19:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我对他也没辙 唯一有用的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.14,0:19:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 门没锁 我就进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 怎么突然来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.31,0:19:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春要我带你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就到此为止 打道回府如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里很吵 好像也没时间轻松地聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你最吵嘛\N但我会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲爱的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 后会有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空我会去你那边走走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了 各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 你是走来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了表示歉意 我来开车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.28,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女从以前就最听波鸟的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说他很崇拜波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.02,0:20:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说波鸟拥有他所想要却没有的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以很崇拜波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说很想珍惜他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前他们也常说正经事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以波鸟可说是绫女的保姆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真这样想的话 行动前先用用大脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.15,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是由希还是不愿打开心胸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.18,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希也不是傻瓜 只是年纪还小罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有很多事情不愿让步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么好心急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.19,0:20:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透和你有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是为别人着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命的专注起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.03,0:20:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是对这样的人没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.84,0:20:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么总能说些讨人喜欢的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女说的话很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是无可救药的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代沟 代沟 代沟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但绫女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于拥有自己所没有的东西的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.99,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能坦然的表现出好感是很棒的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.63,0:21:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们应该能够有所进展的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.68,0:21:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思让你操心了 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样想不是比较愉快吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.52,0:21:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘了问他卖护士或女仆服饰到底是什么店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是色情俱乐部的话题吗

